<section class="about_section layout_padding-bottom">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-6">
                <div class="detail-box">
                    <h2>
                        About us
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        The Global Labor Market Conference (GLMC) leverages analysis, research, and thought leadership to explore evolving landscapes and enable discussions on data, opportunities, and outlooks. We also host and support influential global events where decision-makers come together to discuss changes that aim to future-proof the global labor market.
                    </p>
                    <a href="">
                        Read More
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-7 col-md-6">
                <div class="img-box">
                    <img src="images/p3.jpeg" alt="">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


<section class="about_section layout_padding-bottom">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-6">
                <div class="detail-box">
                    <h2>
                        Vision of the Conference

                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        To highlight the present capabilities of the cultural and creative economy, and explore promising opportunities for achieving sustainable development.

                        Mission of the Conference
                        To stimulate the cultural and creative economy, provide a platform for showcasing outstanding scientific research, and enhance dialogue between experts, researchers, and decision-makers while offering practical recommendations to reach new horizons.

                    </p>
                    <h3>
                        Objectives of the Conference
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        Highlight the role of creativity and innovation in enhancing sustainable development and improving communities.
                        Stimulate the ability of individuals and communities to adapt to rapid changes through the exchange of innovative ideas.
                        Promote dialogue and collaboration between experts and decision-makers to provide practical recommendations that address current issues.
                        Encourage participants to discover their creative potential and make better use of their intellectual energies.

                    </p>

                    <a href="">
                        Read More
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-7 col-md-6">
